Package com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.delpsservice

The i2 Analyze DELPS service provides clients with the ability to interact with data load ELP stage solutions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDelpsService
    A set of methods for interacting with an i2 Analyze DELPS (data load ELP stage) solution, including the ability to synchronize Items in the ELP stage with changing data in an external source.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ElpStageUnavailableException.Fault
    Contains information about the enclosing ElpStageUnavailableException.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ElpStageUnavailableException
    The exception raised when the DELPS service detects that an ELP stage is not responding to messages.

Package com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.delpsservice Description

The i2 Analyze DELPS service provides clients with the ability to interact with data load ELP stage solutions.

The operations supported by the DELPS service are:

Web methodDescription
CreateOrReplaceItems Adds or replaces items in the item store of a specified ELP stage.
CreateOrReplaceItemsXml Creates items from platform-compatible XML, and then adds or replaces them in the item store of a specified ELP stage.
DeleteItems Deletes items with specified keys from the item store of a specified ELP stage.
PurgeItems Purges items with specified keys from the item store of a specified ELP stage.

Since:
5.0
